♪ Lies reflect in water's gleam ♪

278
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:43,060
♪ Traces of existence
can never be erased ♪

279
00:14:43,340 --> 00:14:46,620
♪ How to find the self I can't reclaim ♪

280
00:14:48,940 --> 00:14:56,000
♪ Fly away, hear she says ♪

281
00:14:56,080 --> 00:15:00,036
♪ She'll fly out from
thorns of woven lies ♪

282
00:15:00,060 --> 00:15:03,636
♪ Pierce the fog,
shatter this dream tonight ♪

283
00:15:03,660 --> 00:15:06,596
♪ Burn like fire ♪

284
00:15:06,620 --> 00:15:10,040
♪ Just burn like fire ♪

285
00:15:10,250 --> 00:15:14,130
♪ The maze in the abyss starts to clear ♪

286
00:15:14,180 --> 00:15:16,866
♪ Yet night keep on whispering ♪

287
00:15:16,890 --> 00:15:20,030
♪ Surrender to fate,
no clear direction ahead ♪

288
00:15:20,310 --> 00:15:23,810
♪ She will rise as the dawn
that breaks the darkness ♪

289
00:15:23,890 --> 00:15:30,340
♪ Never slowing down,
for tomorrow cannot be stopped ♪

290
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:34,316
♪ Surrender to love and find the way ♪

291
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:37,860
♪ Even if fate tries to forget her ♪

292
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:44,610
♪ Never despair,
for the heart burns with endless light ♪

293
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:46,880
♪ Waiting for dawn ♪

